

INSTALL
=======

* Prerequisites:

  - Python 2.6 (!)
  - LLVM 2.4
  - LLVM-PY 0.5
  - For generating the documentation:
    
    Sphinx 0.5, or current development:
    
      - To check out:
        hg clone http://bitbucket.org/birkenfeld/sphinx
        
      - To update:
        hg pull http://bitbucket.org/birkenfeld/sphinx

